软件包 cn.domob.android.ads

接口摘要
DomobAdEventListener Call method "setAdEventListener" of a instance of DomobAdView to set event listener.
DomobAdListener An interface for listening Domob banner ads.
DomobFeedsAdListener  
DomobInterstitialAdListener An interface for listening Domob interstitial ads.
DomobRTSplashAdListener An interface for listening Domob real time splash ads.
DomobSplashAdListener An interface for listening Domob splash ads.
 

类摘要
DomobAdManager A class for managing Domob ads.
DomobAdView A class for invoking Domob banner ads.
DomobFeedsAdView A class for invoking Domob Feeds ads.
DomobInterstitialAd A class for invoking Domob interstitial ads.
DomobRTSplashAd A class for invoking Domob real time splash ads.
DomobSplashAd A class for invoking Domob splash ads.
DomobUpdater A class for reminding update.
 

枚举摘要

DomobInterstitialAd.BorderType  
DomobSplashAd.DomobSplashMode Domob Splash Mode
